    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E39 M5 represents the zenith of the sports sedan, featuring the legendary S62 5.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Mechanically pristine, the engine delivers a linear power band with a 7,000 RPM redline, supported by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson strut front end have been maintained to original tolerances, ensuring the communicative steering and chassis balance remain razor-sharp. With zero oil leaks, a reinforced subframe, and flawless compression across all eight cylinders, this collector-grade example is a testament to meticulous preventative maintenance. An absolute turnkey masterpiece for the purist.",
      "price": 49500.0,
