      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time-capsule' specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior is flawless, featuring laser-straight body panels and original paint that retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from rock chips, swirls, or parking lot blemishes. The wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with deep tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is in showroom condition; the leather upholstery still possesses its factory matte finish and 'new car' scent, with no bolster wear or sun-fading on the dash. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio. It delivers a tight, responsive driving experience that feels identical to its first day on the road. This is an investment-grade example for a collector who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
